title: I Have Tried, But I'm Not Being Satisfied
itunes:title: I Have Tried, But I'm Not Being Satisfied
description:
Dear Steve and Miss strawberry, I have been dating my boyfriend for over a year and I love him so much. We hardly ever argue or fight because we live an hour away from each other so when we are together we make the best of our time. We do everything together except one big thing when we do see each other.
